502
00:57:05,980 --> 00:57:06,900
Yes.

503
00:57:07,619 --> 00:57:09,219
And did you see the fight?

504
00:57:11,580 --> 00:57:12,659
No.

505
00:57:13,699 --> 00:57:15,900
