578
01:07:30,540 --> 01:07:31,619
No?

579
01:07:33,380 --> 01:07:34,299
Thanks.

580
01:07:36,060 --> 01:07:37,020
You want to come in?

581
01:07:38,179 --> 01:07:39,739
Get inside! Shoo! Get in!

582
01:07:41,739 --> 01:07:43,139
Get inside!

583
