604
01:09:36,299 --> 01:09:38,299
- Afternoon!
- Good afternoon.

605
01:09:40,299 --> 01:09:41,860
I'm Niki's father.

606
01:09:43,900 --> 01:09:46,259
You didn't tell your grandmother?

607
01:09:50,060 --> 01:09:55,339
